Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H222A9A&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark! Demonic Invention!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How is research proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark, the lab tells\Nus they'll need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Much too slow! Tell\Nthem to hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark refers to the research of world famous\NNanbara Souichirou, director of GOD R&D.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,His research aims to build a device capable of\Ntransforming any matter on Earth into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls it the RS Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With the RS Device installed inside him, King\NDark will have the energy to run rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The day King Dark arises will\Nbe the day this world falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamai, I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No objections from me, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me if something's\Nworrying you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamai--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've removed all\Nof GOD's bugs from this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please tell me! The RS Device's\Nblueprints are finished, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiots still haven't realised\Nthere's microphones in their buttons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guessed it. The RS\NDevice's blueprints are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I shudder when\NI think about its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD will use it\Nas a demonic weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the right hands, it could\Nbe a gift from the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A demonic invention or\Na gift from the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. GOD has my daughter's...\Nmy only daughter's life by a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The RS Device is\Nfinished? Report to King Dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanbara hid the fact that he's already\Ncompleted the RS Device's blueprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them out of him, Toad Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a brain worthy of Japan's\Ngreatest thief, Ishikawa Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how a burglary\Ngenius always gets his mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the boasting for after the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa Goemon was a master of Iga\Nstyle ninjutsu, and I have inherited his skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Nanbara's daughter...\NStart by using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The summer holidays at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to my house in Karuizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm going to Hawaii!\N-What about you, Nanbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie's dad's a big shot!\NProbably Europe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to show\Noff about going to Hawai'i!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right!\N-I meant Hawai, in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Having trouble\Nwith your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not taking you on holiday until\Nyou've done your homework, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! My dad'll take me anywhere I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What a nice dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... Why do you look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your dad now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to come straight home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say anything about the doctor's\Nwork and your life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, we're watching\Nyou around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go! Let my dad go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Just live your life as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want anyone getting suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's already suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy from the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even try it!\NNo one escapes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help!\N-Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're from King Dark's\Narmy... Put her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... You think you\Ncan defeat Toad Goemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be glad to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! Flaming Toad Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon! You're\Nnot going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My Toad Oil deflects\Nall your punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even feel them!\NNow it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goemon Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving Rie comes first...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon! We'll\Nsettle this next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-You'll be safe here.\N-You must've been so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To think King Dark got his hands on a\Nworld famous scientist like Dr. Nanbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of research might he be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope my dad's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hand over Rie or Nanbara's dead\N--Toad Goemon."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-He's already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad's in trouble!\N-Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we've got\Na really strong friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Are you trying\Nto ruin our research!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubbish! Don't try to pull\Nthe wool over my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the RS Device's blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're still not complete!\N-Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand them over if you value\Nyour assistant's life, Nanbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, doctor! The RS\NDevice is a gift from the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, there's no need for violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't hand it over? What if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the other one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait!\N-Don't worry! It's just one life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No price, no research,\Nis worth a human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, just hand them over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to scare\Nme with that cheap toy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It does look like a\Ntoy, doesn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The computers all vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just the power\Nof a prototype RS Device!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mini RS Device...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, doctor! Quickly,\Nrun! Hurry, doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't protect the blueprints alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I\Ncan't let GOD have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've only one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara divided the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Dr. Nanbara!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No Toad Goemon either. Did\Nsomething happen to the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Dr. Nanbara mailed eight of\Nthe blueprint pieces to eight colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it... I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie! Rie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they take her away\Nwhile she was alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamai! You're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I know where\Nthey're holding Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You do? Show me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, but why don't\Nyou let me look after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...But Tamai, that monster\Nburned your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A prototype RS Device is even\Nbetter than the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is\Nbuild a bigger version!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect Dr. Nanbara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, X Rider!\NJust in time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that weird ball for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late! X Rider...\NThis is your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I removed the ignition. I was\Nwondering when you would notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast you! X Rider... I'll get\Nthe blueprints after I defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that device, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The RS Device... It can process\Nthe energy of any material.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A demonic weapon in GOD's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonic...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD forced me to develop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I fled, hoping I could turn\Nit into a gift from the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie's at Tachibana's coffee shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa Goemon was a prodigious shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold his Iga style wood technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can find me, X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast! You found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The oil again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Rider's punch is\Nnothing against my oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Flaming Toad Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Windmill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave you alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... believe you're on the\Nside of justice, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I split the blueprints into nine,\Nand... sent eight to my colleagues...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please... protect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doctor!\N-Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He split it into nine... but\Nsent it to eight colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke...\N-Rie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad must have put it in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rie...\N-I knew dad better than anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did he have to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rie, I promise you and your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep his blueprints safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let GOD lay a finger on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Find all nine pieces, including\Nthe one Jin Keisuke has!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rely on Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth's doom? Or mankind's salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible battle for the torn\Nblueprints is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(0,5)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The RS Device's blueprints have been\Nsplit into nine pieces and hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's Scorpion Geronimo sets his sights\Non a young hiker with one of the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Vengeful Ogre Geronimo! Silent Assault!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider